cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI

The paper deals with improving lip-reading models using deep learning architectures, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The use of a 3D Morphable Model (3DMM) for generating synthetic facial data also involves multimedia (cs.MM) and machine learning (cs.LG) techniques. Finally, the proposed approach involves training a neural network, which falls under artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
